snippet.title: Stela Announcement Trailer [2019] | Wishlist Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Add Stela to your Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1048600/Stela/ 

Stela is launching on Xbox One on October 17th! It will also launch on Apple Arcade in the coming weeks, and will be available on PC in Q1 2020. 

Stela is a cinematic, atmospheric platformer about a young woman witnessing the final days of a mysterious ancient world.

Stela is being developed by Halo Infinite co-developer, Vancouver-based game studio, SkyBox Labs. The title will debut at GDC 2019 as an official selection in Microsoft’s ID@Xbox Developer Showcase.

http://www.stela-game.com
https://www.skyboxlabs.com
